Nova marca registada TPC

A empresa The Pokémon Company registou a marca “Momowarou” da “Pecharunt” em Pokémon Scarlet & Violet.
https://vxtwitter.com/pokexperto/status/1737437249124372926

#MarcaRegistada #TPC #PokémonScarlet&Violet

